metadata.name: Genesis Talk 1
metadata.description:
Since the inception of Web3 Talks, we have spoken with dozens of great web3 founders. They shared their hard-earned knowledge & experience to inspire the next generation of hackers.

"Genesis Talk" is the NFT inspired by the talk we wish we had. With the guest that inspired us all. 

Mint "Genesis Talk" to celebrate the crypto history and be able to join the upcoming Web3 Talks community.

To get the info when the community kicks off, provide your e-mail address or Twitter handle.
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1-Ia69v7yXFC5Nx7DZMNZ45Q77ZUrEB542oJda3TnIdU/edit
